    <item>
      <title>特朗普未能推翻纽约州的定罪，将于 1 月 10 日接受宣判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/trump-loses-latest-bid-to-overturn-new-york-criminal-conviction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普已被要求于 1 月 10 日出庭接受封口费刑事案件的宣判，但纽约州法官表示这位当选总统不会入狱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/trump-loses-latest-bid-to-overturn-new-york-criminal-conviction</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 20:57:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>约翰逊在与反对派进行最后谈判后赢得众议院议长选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/johnson-wins-house-speaker-vote-after-late-talks-with-holdouts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党人迈克·约翰逊在经过最后一刻的一系列谈判后，克服了少数但至关重要的保守派强硬派的阻力，并得到了当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的关键支持，再次当选众议院议长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/johnson-wins-house-speaker-vote-after-late-talks-with-holdouts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 19:35:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党的约翰逊试图在第一轮选举中扭转局势，赢得议长职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/johnson-appears-to-fall-short-of-votes-needed-to-win-speaker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党人迈克·约翰逊似乎未能连任众议院议长，这促使共和党推迟投票，而他和他的盟友则努力扭转选票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/johnson-appears-to-fall-short-of-votes-needed-to-win-speaker</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 18:36:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
